{
  "texts": [
    "At the same time, it is scalable to process large numbers of publications.",
    "As we have seen, such an approach is feasible with a performance similar to or even better in comparison to other current solutions like the approach of Natukunda et al.",
    "However, it should be noted that the performance varied considerably depending on which of the 10 + 1 data sets were used.",
    "Further applications of LLMs in literature analysisWhile we investigated LLMs for evaluating the relevance of publications and in particular for title and abstract screening, it is being discussed how these models may be used for a variety of tasks in literature analysis [58,59].",
    "For example, Wang et al."
  ]
